#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:52
msgid ""
"With the *Bounding Box Center* pivot point active, the *Cursor to "
"Selected* option will snap the 3D cursor to the center of the bounding "
"box surrounding the objects' centers."
msgstr ""
"Avec le point pivot actif sur le centre de la boîte d'encombrement, "
"l'option *Cursor to Selected* va coller le Curseur 3D au centre de la "
"boîte d'encombrement autour du centre des objets."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:55
msgid ""
"When the *Median Point* pivot point is selected, *Cursor to Selected* "
"will snap the 3D cursor to the `median "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Median>`__ of the object centers."
msgstr ""
"Quand le point de pivot *Median Point* est sélectionné, *Cursor to "
"Selected* va fixer le Curseur 3D sur la `médiane "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Median>`__ du centre des objets."

